Author: Shaun Wilkinson [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Shaun Wilkinson <shaunpwilkinson@gmail.com>
Description: A package for developing phylogenetic trees as
    deeply-nested lists ("dendrogram" objects).
    Contains functions for bi-directional conversion between dendrogram and
    "phylo" objects
    (see Paradis et al (2004) <doi:10.1093/bioinformatics/btg412>),
    as well as several tools for command-line tree
    manipulation and import/export via Newick parenthetic text.
License: GPL-3
